      "author": "liaocaoxuezhe",
      "description": "## Analogy 1.1.2\n\n- Adds multi-tab local semantic search in the sidebar.\n- Adds result-card exploration tabs that exclude already-seen result paths for broader discovery.\n- Improves local service initialization so concurrent startup requests share the same initialization flow.\n- Improves local vector search backfill behavior when muted or excluded paths reduce result count.\n- Keeps public release assets focused on the Obsidian plugin and local RAG/MCP runtime package.\n\nUpload assets are the standard Obsidian files: `main.js`, `manifest.json`, and `styles.css`. The full zip includes the local RAG/MCP package files.\n",
