      "author": "liaocaoxuezhe",
      "description": "## Analogy 1.1.0\r\n\r\nMajor usability release for community installs.\r\n\r\n- Adds a settings-page local RAG runtime installer for `@huggingface/transformers` and `onnxruntime-node`.\r\n- Resolves npm lookup issues when Obsidian is launched from macOS GUI environments with a limited PATH.\r\n- Refresh now reinitializes local services after runtime installation.\r\n- Clears stale runtime errors after successful Chroma/vector/embedding initialization.\r\n- Keeps the Obsidian community release assets as `main.js`, `manifest.json`, and `styles.css`.\r\n\r\nInstall/update through Obsidian using the three standard assets. For the full local RAG/MCP package, download the full zip asset.",
